    "description": "《地下城卷轴（战术版）》是以小队形式作战的攻城游戏，采用了老虎机机制，并且可以观看木偶剧！招募新的小队成员，他们每个人都有内置的老虎机卷轴，你需要带领他们击败“大魔王”...在遍布敌人阻击要塞的地图上尽情探险吧，看看命运卡给你带来什么好运，击败可怕凶残的 Boss，体验丰富多彩的探险之旅！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在探险旅途中收集招募点券，招募新的小队成员</h2>《地下城卷轴（战术版）》的每个回合都有 12 个不同的角色，让您在探险过程中随意招募。要招募新队员，你需要从倒下的敌人身上收集灵魂碎片、使用命运卡或在商店中购买招募点券。如果小队成员陷入了战斗，他们可能会死亡，而你则需要招募新的小队成员才能继续探险。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901030/extras/8b6cb9076943682e6e59d1aaa35fe557.poster.avif?t=1651517007\" width=626 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901030/extras/8b6cb9076943682e6e59d1aaa35fe557.webm?t=1651517007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901030/extras/8b6cb9076943682e6e59d1aaa35fe557.mp4?t=1651517007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >老虎机决定了你在每个回合的技能</h2>每个小队成员都有自己的独特老虎机。在每个回合中，老虎机都将通过卷轴为你提供 3 种随机技能。在每个回合中都要做出最佳决策，不然难以统治战场。如果出现 3 个相同的图标，你的小队成员就可以施放独有的头奖技能。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901030/extras/52d61bdbe6fa4460832d9c0d3b2ba94d.poster.avif?t=1651517007\" width=626 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901030/extras/52d61bdbe6fa4460832d9c0d3b2ba94d.webm?t=1651517007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901030/extras/52d61bdbe6fa4460832d9c0d3b2ba94d.mp4?t=1651517007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901030/extras/0419185f3e9b752bf1faaab8de889900.poster.avif?t=1651517007\" width=626 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901030/extras/0419185f3e9b752bf1faaab8de889900.webm?t=1651517007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901030/extras/0419185f3e9b752bf1faaab8de889900.mp4?t=1651517007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游历整个地图，完成奖励目标，努力击败“大魔王”</h2>每个回合开始的时候都使用随机生成的地图。你的目标是击败所有 3 个 Boss。每次击败一个 Boss，你都需要重新启动地图，有些走过的路线会消失。击败地图上的 3 个 Boss 之后，如果完成至少 3 个奖励目标，就可以在结束时解锁“大魔王”飞行。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901030/extras/5d24c3e3b6c2fd8d9e462ce9e85a1974.poster.avif?t=1651517007\" width=626 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901030/extras/5d24c3e3b6c2fd8d9e462ce9e85a1974.webm?t=1651517007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901030/extras/5d24c3e3b6c2fd8d9e462ce9e85a1974.mp4?t=1651517007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>主要特色：<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>可以招募/解锁 24 个角色<br></li><li>30 种敌人<br></li><li>6 个 Boss<br></li><li>100 张命运卡<br></li><li>40 种遗物。<br></li><li> 26 个特色竞技场<br></li><li>按照程序生成的木偶剧表演，为您讲述故事发展脉络</li></ul><br>社区：<br>加入 Discord Server，和社区成员讨论游戏策略，了解游戏最新消息。",
